email_context.summary: There are three emails that require attention. The first one is from Rui Zhang, inviting for an article or abstract submission for the 12th Conference on Energy, Environment and Earth Sciences with a deadline on September 10, 2025. The second email is from Kierra Jewell, notifying about a document in the KFS action list that needs attention. The third email is from Francesca, discussing about meetings in August and confirming a meeting on Tuesday or Monday afternoon.
